		"description":{
			"value":"<p><i>The radiance of this holy symbol both lights your way and helps you overcome the challenges that block the path.</i></p><p><b>Implement</b><b>:</b> Holy symbol</p>\n<p><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p><b>Critical:</b> +4d6 radiant critical damage</p>\n<p><b>Power - Encounter (Minor Action)</b></p><p>Effect: The candle casts bright light in a radius of 4 squares. The light lasts until you extinguish it as a minor action or until you are no longer holding the candle.</p><p><b>Power - Encounter (Immediate Interrupt)</b></p><p>Trigger: An ally within 5 squares of you fails a skill check while the candle is lit.</p><p>Effect: The candle's light is extinguished, and the ally gains a power bonus to the skill check equal to 2 + the candle's enhancement bonus.</p>",
